# Vibe Matcher Prototype
This notebook builds a mini vibe-based recommender. It uses OpenAI embeddings (`text-embedding-3-large`) if you provide `OPENAI_API_KEY`.

**How to use:**

1. If you want to use OpenAI, set your API key as an environment variable in your system or Colab.
2. Run the cells below. The notebook includes a deterministic TF-IDF+SVD fallback for offline use.

