## Notes
- To use OpenAI embeddings, set the environment variable `OPENAI_API_KEY` and run `python -c "from src.eval import run_tests; run_tests(prefer_openai=True)"` or edit `src/eval.py` to call `run_tests(prefer_openai=True)`. 
- `text-embedding-3-large` is used in the embedder wrapper; costs may apply when calling OpenAI.
